What is this 'The 50 Project' DPH keeps referring to?  Well, unless 
Telvido blows the secret, it'll be a mystery until this board is dried 
up for topics except for Tournament rules.  I'll put it this way:  
that topic will take a loonnnggg ttttiiiiimmmmmmeeeeeee to cover.  

Beyond saying that, I will say one purpose of the mystery is to 
covertly convince you guys to keep posting messages so you avoid the 
big mystery.  Just joking.  Meanwhile, feel free to try and guess what 
 'The 50 Project' is about.
